text: 33rd Street is a station on the IRT Lexington Avenue Line of the New York City Subway. Located at the intersection of 33rd Street and Park Avenue in Murray Hill, Manhattan. It is served by the 6 train. After this station, the next stations will be Grand Central 42nd Street and 28th Street. ==References== Category:New York City Subway stations Category:Manhattan
title: 33rd Street station (IRT Lexington Avenue Line)
